WEBVTT

00:00:59.399 --> 00:01:01.131
They scare us.

00:01:01.131 --> 00:01:03.116
But the choices they make

00:01:03.116 --> 00:01:05.286
have dramatic outcomes

00:01:05.286 --> 00:01:08.274
that influence us all.

00:01:08.274 --> 00:01:11.609
So I am here today because I think we need hackers,

00:01:11.609 --> 00:01:15.192
and in fact, they just might be

00:01:15.192 --> 00:01:19.532
the immune system for the information age.

00:01:19.532 --> 00:01:21.565
Sometimes they make us sick,

00:01:21.565 --> 00:01:24.920
but they also find those hidden threats

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.244
in our world,

00:01:26.244 --> 00:01:29.089
and they make us fix it.

00:01:29.089 --> 00:01:31.447
I knew that I might get hacked